text: Recently I’ve met a few unrelated 12yos who had all turned 12 since after the 12+ EUA. So, initially ineligible and aged into eligibility. 100% of them had gotten the first dose of the #CovidVaccine within 2-3 days of their birthday. @DrDanSchumacher, this is leadership!

As someone who is vaccinated and mandated in some places to wear a mask, why should I care more to protect the unvaccinated than they are willing to care for themselves? #COVID19 #CovidVaccine #MaskMandate
